{"id": "1413501464508366868", "channel_id": "1326453691527594035", "author_id": "896400240192675850", "author_name": "hskzu", "content": "[Gameplay Adjustment]\n● Awakener \"Kathigu-Ra\"\n    ○ Exalt \"World-Ending Inferno\": Damage decreased from 12 to 10.\n    ○ Skill \"Death Bullet\": Base DMG increased from 6 to 8, growth DMG reduced from 2 to 1.\n● Awakener \"Doll: Inferno\"\n    ○ Skill \"Genius' Foresight\": Redo. Consumes 1 point of Arithmetica. Choose: Gain 2 Arithmetica or draw 1 card. Prepare.\n    ○ Skill \"Humanity Observation Trial\": HP Recovery reduced from 18 to 16, DMG reduced from 12 to 10.\n● Wheel of Destiny and Posse\n    ○ Wheel of Destiny \"Pale Descendant\": Arithmetica cost increases from 2 to 3.\n    ○ Wheel of Destiny \"Analysis of Death\": Arithmetica cost reduced from 3 to 2.\n    ○ Wheel of Destiny \"Fate Roulette\": The increase in damage, healing, and shield effects from \"Skill\" is raised from 5~25% to 10~30%.\n    ○ Posse \"Derison of Destiny\": Redo. Choose a friendly unit to gain 1 layer of Charge and 1 Onyx Plume; for every 2 fallen characters, gain an additional layer of Charge.", "timestamp": "2025-09-05T12:30:10.726000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "💀", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}]}
